        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1A–D. Texella martensi n. sp., holotype male. A–B Habitus (A ventrolateral, B dorsolateral). C Ventral view showing spur on trochanter IV (white arrow) and anterior part of genital operculum with slightly protruding ventral plate (black arrow). D Dorsal view of ocular region and palpi. Scale bars: 0.5 mm (A–B), 0.2 mm (C–D)." ;
